Package program3

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • program3.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Instate, International, Outstate
    abstract class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    Abstract class for shared functionality between student types. Includes compareTo implementation, toString of shared variables, and declares an abstract tuitionDue() method.
